# close-brace-deeply-indented

## Input

```
s {
  k v
            }

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..24
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..24
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "s"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    SPACE@4..6 "  "
    ENTRY@6..10
      WORD_KEY@6..7
        WORD@6..7 "k"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      LINE_STRING@8..9
        STRING@8..9 "v"
      NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
    SPACE@10..22 "            "
    CLOSE_BRACE@22..23 "}"
    NEWLINE@23..24 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "s",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{",
            items: [
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@6..7 "k",
                    },
                    value: LineString {
                        string: STRING@8..9 "v",
                    },
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@22..23 "}",
        },
    ],
}
```

